jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolMIB.name: jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolMIB
jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolMIB.contactinfo: Juniper Technical Assistance Center Juniper Networks, Inc. 1194 N. Mathilda Avenue Sunnyvale, CA 94089 E-mail: support@juniper.net HTTP://www.juniper.net
jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolMIB.description: This module defines the NAT-src-pool-specific MIB for Juniper Enterprise Logical-System (LSYS) security profiles. Juniper documentation is recommended as the reference. The LSYS security profile provides various static and dynamic resource management by observing resource quota limits. Security NAT-src-pool resource is the focus in this MIB.

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolTable.description: LSYSPROFILE NAT-src-pool objects for NAT-src-pool resource consumption per LSYS.

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolEntry.description: An entry in NAT-src-pool resource table.

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolProfileName.name: jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolProfileName
jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolProfileName.description: The security profile name string for the LSYS.

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolUsage.name: jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolUsage
jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolUsage.description: The current resource usage count for the LSYS.

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolReserved.name: jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolReserved
jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolReserved.description: The reserved resource count for the LSYS.

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolMaximum.name: jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolMaximum

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolUsedAmount.name: jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolUsedAmount

jnxLsysSpNATsrcpoolMaxQuota.description: The NAT-src-pool resource maximum quota for the whole device for all LSYS.
